description:
Carl Barks Digital Archive:

Articles and Documentaries
with Bonus

The 15 GB collection had to be winrar 
compressed because the original 
torrent size was 330kb and was blocked
from being uploaded by Piratebay.

Articles:

1. Interviews
2. Carl Barks Fan Webpages
3. Fan Newsletters
4. Duckburg Maps
5. Essays
6. Carl Barks books:
a. Donald Duck
by M Blitz 
b. CB and the Art of the Comic Book
by M. Barrier
c. CB and the Disney Comic Book
by T. Andrae
An Informal Biography of Scrooge McDuck
by J. Chalker
d. How to Read Donald Duck
by Dorfman and Mattleart
7. Gottfried Helnwein essays on Carl Barks

Documentaries:

1975 The Duck Man An Interview with Carl Barks
1981 Carl Barks TV Interview USA
1991 Disney Legends Carl Barks
1994 Carl Barks in Denmark
1994 Carl Barks Meets His Fans
1994 The Overstreet World of Comic Books
1996 Carl Barks The Duck Maestro
1997 Happy Birthday Carl Barks
1999 Duckburg is Everywhere
2006 The Art and Animation of Carl Barks
2009 Carl Barks The Good Duck Artist

Bonus:
Lots of good Carl Barks related stuff!

